cat > UI_AGENT.md <<'EOF'
# UI Design Agent Instructions

Before creating any new UI:

1. Read:
   - ui/design_principles.md
   - ui/design_decisions.md
   - ui/design-system/components.md
   - ui/screens/screen_inventory.md
   - ui/flows/user_flows.md

2. Check:
   - Existing screens
   - Existing components
   - Existing UX patterns

3. Avoid:
   - Recreating existing screens
   - Introducing duplicate components
   - Violating design system rules

4. Every new screen must include:
   - User goal
   - Success path
   - Failure states
   - Empty states
   - Loading states
   - Accessibility requirements
   - Responsive behavior

5. Every design change must update:
   - screen_inventory.md
   - design_decisions.md
   - frontend_mapping.md

6. Maintain consistency with all previous design decisions.
EOF

echo "Enterprise UI/UX framework created."
